summary: DIVERGENT AGENT (Bucky Barnes x reader) - Chapter 3 (on Wattpad) https://my.w.tt/zg1DSowYsW   The Avengers and S.H.I.E.L.D. are...
caption:
DIVERGENT AGENT (Bucky Barnes x reader) - Chapter 3 (on Wattpad) https://my.w.tt/zg1DSowYsW 

 The Avengers and S.H.I.E.L.D. are in need of new agents. As every year, they bring recruits from all over the country, to find new members and agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. There is always one spot open to become an actual Avenger. When new recruits come to the compound, the system changes and the tasks become more difficult. A young woman, fighting for a spot to become an agent, brings an unknown power that makes her a target for any enemy around the world. 

Bucky Barnes x female!reader fanfiction 

Inspired by Divergent series (but it is not a crossover). 

Disclaimer: I do not own the characters, they belong to Marvel Comics and MCU. 

 Warning: strong language, violence, possible nudity and sex I will be putting notes ahead if any NSFW chapter will be uploaded. But the story will be marked as Mature content.

tags: even activision blizzard had the balls to make not one but two of their most iconic characters gay
summary: Marvel could have made their first openly gay character important and memorable and truly groundbreaking. They could have had bi...
body: Marvel could have made their first openly gay character important and memorable and truly groundbreaking. They could have had bi Valkyrie. They could have had bi Captain America. They could have had lesbian Carol fucking Danvers for crying out loud. They could have something brave and uplifting and given millions of queer fans a role model they can look up to and be inspired by, but they were cowards, and now they have to live with the disgrace of their first openly gay character being nameless not-even-a-minute-of-screen-time Joe Russo, so in my book they just shot themselves in the foot
